;************* Cshow.key ***************
; A stuffit/stuffkey command file to get Compuserve's Cshow program,
; standard (non-slide show) version to display a slide show anyway.
; To use, run "stuffkey /f:cshow.key", then run Cshow as you normally do.
; I suggest you put these commands in a batch file, which I have 
; conveniently supplied!  (see Slides.bat) 
; J.Geist 10Oct92
;****************
; Delay a bit, select all files {F9}, select show all {F8), then do it 
+0 +4 {F9} +1 {F8} +1 +0        
